# 😎 Understanding and using Build Tools 😎



** ⚒️Tools and Topics covered⚒️ **
    - Overview of Build tools. (Maven, Gradle)
    - Maven - Architecture, Plugins, Archetypes, Commands
    - Integration of Jacoco Plugin for Code Coverage


** 🧠Key Learnings🧠 **
    - Application build : Compile the code + Create artifacts + Perform unit testing 
    - pom.xml : Project Object Model
    - Maven respository : https://mvnrepository.com/ ( Contains dependicies and plugins)
    - Build environment (VM)
